    "tier": 1,
    "desc": "I did 2 sequential fixes.",
    "body": "Commits:\n\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/ana-lists/commit/cabe8a208b7f92407333d4559d132b8ed3a51a11\">cabe8a2</a>: fix: move client bundle build step before deployment to ensure proper deployment\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/dai/ana-lists/commit/f15e7b7b6cd713228d27ffca668b9bc0c5394791\">f15e7b7</a>: fix: simplify deployment condition and add Cloudflare secrets verification step",
